  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>This game accurs in the same universe of Heroes of Time</strong></i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990400/extras/63a98b71e9df76191a326c50d8ed36b9.poster.avif?t=1742271327\" width=544 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990400/extras/63a98b71e9df76191a326c50d8ed36b9.webm?t=1742271327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990400/extras/63a98b71e9df76191a326c50d8ed36b9.mp4?t=1742271327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A CLASSIC JRPG. Containing all the elements of a turn-based RPG. Elliot, Louis and Kary will be our heroes, facing a man named Lars and other challenges that will be awating for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rumors have speculated on the possibility of a frightening creature emerging. Indeed, may religious texts had spoken of the demon's arrival, and some rumors were based on such prophecies. However, the efforts of Lars, among the elite soldiers of King Grimfur's army, has helped to make the emergence a grim reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990400/extras/b7bc634e1f0ad518cdac500d0b74703c.poster.avif?t=1742271327\" width=546 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990400/extras/b7bc634e1f0ad518cdac500d0b74703c.webm?t=1742271327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990400/extras/b7bc634e1f0ad518cdac500d0b74703c.mp4?t=1742271327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three soldiers work for world peace. They had established themselves in Ágaris, and other portions of the world. One of their stated tasks to revive Rion. King Grimfur has a secret confidence for Rion to become in composition of the ever-grown armies of darkness. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the fate of the world hanging in the balance, it is up to you, intrepid heroes, to defeat evil!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>This game accurs in the same universe of Heroes of Time</strong></i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990400/extras/63a98b71e9df76191a326c50d8ed36b9.poster.avif?t=1742271327\" width=544 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990400/extras/63a98b71e9df76191a326c50d8ed36b9.webm?t=1742271327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990400/extras/63a98b71e9df76191a326c50d8ed36b9.mp4?t=1742271327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A CLASSIC JRPG. Containing all the elements of a turn-based RPG. Elliot, Louis and Kary will be our heroes, facing a man named Lars and other challenges that will be awating for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rumors have speculated on the possibility of a frightening creature emerging. Indeed, may religious texts had spoken of the demon's arrival, and some rumors were based on such prophecies. However, the efforts of Lars, among the elite soldiers of King Grimfur's army, has helped to make the emergence a grim reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990400/extras/b7bc634e1f0ad518cdac500d0b74703c.poster.avif?t=1742271327\" width=546 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990400/extras/b7bc634e1f0ad518cdac500d0b74703c.webm?t=1742271327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990400/extras/b7bc634e1f0ad518cdac500d0b74703c.mp4?t=1742271327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three soldiers work for world peace. They had established themselves in Ágaris, and other portions of the world. One of their stated tasks to revive Rion. King Grimfur has a secret confidence for Rion to become in composition of the ever-grown armies of darkness. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the fate of the world hanging in the balance, it is up to you, intrepid heroes, to defeat evil!</p>",
